Where to Watch

This epic sword-and-sorcery spectacle, set against the fall of the Roman Empire, follows the adventures of Rome's 12-year-old emperor and his battle against a ruthless warlord. Colin Firth and Ben Kingsley star. Aishwarya Rai, Peter Mullan. Directed by Doug Lefler.
